use the following story.</NOTE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Associated Press reported erroneously
Tuesday that Manufacturers Hanover Corp. declared a regular
quarterly stock dividend of 32 cents on each of its common shares.
The correct amount was 82 cents per share for stockholders of
record Oct. 1 and payable Oct. 25.
</TEXT>
